<title>Claire's | Safe, Sterile, Hypoallergenic Ear Piercing</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Claire’s provides safe, sterile, hypoallergenic ear piercing using the latest technology, backed by 40+ years of experience and over 110 million ears pierced. We offer a wide range of earrings for sensitive ears and every occasion, plus trending jewelry, hair accessories, beauty, toys, and more in store."/>
